senselogic.sitevision.api.webresource

Interface WebResourceFactory


  • @Requireable(value="WebResourceFactory")
public interface WebResourceFactory
    Factory for creating instances of web resource utilities.

    An instance of the Sitevision class implementing this interface can be obtained via Utils.getWebResourceFactory(). See Utils for how to obtain an instance of the Utils interface.

    Since:
    Sitevision 4.2
